  <strong> Performance </strong>
  <p>
    The Xbox ROG Ally can play triple A at 80 to 60 FPS but you must have acsess
    to a power outlet to get it without the device pluged in, you will only get
    50 to 40 FPS the Xbox ROG Ally has a 120 hertz sound and 1080p display
  </p>
  <strong> Playstation Exclusives </strong>
  <p>
    The Xbox ROG Ally can play Playstation exclusives, but it is through the
    steam store. Playstation exclusives will not come day one release though.
    Playstation exclusives will come withen nine to twelve months after release,
    and then they will be avalible to purchase on the steam store.
  </p>
